sequenceDiagram
    actor C as Consumer
    participant U as USDC
    participant R as AtriumRegistry
    participant T as Treasury (pull)
    participant P as Parent creator (pull)
    participant K as Skill creator (pull)

    C->>U: approve(R, price)
    C->>R: invokeSkill(skillId)
    R->>U: transferFrom(C, R, price)
    Note over R: protocolCut = price * feeBps / 10000
    R->>T: withdrawable[treasury] += protocolCut
    Note over R: distributable = price - protocolCut
    loop each declared parent i
        R->>P: withdrawable[parent_i] += distributable * bps_i / 10000
    end
    R->>K: withdrawable[creator] += remainder
    Note over R,K: sum of credits == price (conservation)
    K-->>R: withdraw()
    R-->>K: transfer(creator, amount)
